Class IdentedWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.ifmo.ctddev.panin.implementor.IdentedWriter

  • class IdentedWriter
extends java.lang.Object
    This wrapper around BufferedReader allows to easily write indented output, as programmers always do.
